text: Jacobean may refer to: * Jacobean architecture * Jacobean English (the language used in the King James Version of the Bible) * Jacobean era * Jacobean literature * Jacobean theatre * An adjectival form of the name James, particular in relation to the biblical Epistle of James ==See also== * Jacobian (disambiguation) * Jacobin (disambiguation) * Jacobite (disambiguation) * Jacobitism th:จาโคไบท์
title: Jacobean
